modName: PitFall the lost expedition map mod By Shadow0987
summary: From the game PitFall the lost expedition this adds the map from that game to explore in skyrim. This you can explore a big jungle with natives and evil natives and animals
descriptionHtml:
From the game PitFall the lost expedition this adds the map from that game to explore in skyrim. This  you can explore a big jungle with natives and evil natives and animals so go around in the jungle and find out what to do and were to go  

to get to the new place at battle born farm there is a plane go to the back and walk in it 

Dont know were Battle born farm is ? its 1 of the houses nere whiterun so when your at the entrance to whiterun looking at the door at the aver side of whiterun town this is not in the town but there is a plain place and there is a plane in the middle i think there is a map maker you can travel to on the map 

npc
-----------
natives
renegade natives 
wolfs 
trolls
crew man 
icecold natives
and more

also there is secrete treasures everywere that you can sell for a high price

this mod is still in making i have been working on it for a wile then i stop so i may as well post this for people to download

hop you enjoy also try not to get up onto the grass pads
